text: Wayne Barrett: Donald Trump Tried To Bribe Me With An Apartment Friday, 2 October 2015 (18 minutes ago) Years before Donald Trump became a presidential candidate, veteran journalist Wayne Barrett spent more than 10 hours interviewing him for a 1970s Village Voice series (recently republished here and here), which he later expanded into the 1992 book Trump: The Deals and the Downfall.
